message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this fantastic product.  Given its value, I'm happy to start the conversation at $22,000.
Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am only able to offer $15,000 for it.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your perspective, but I'm confident this product is worth more. How about we meet in the middle at $18,000?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your persistence. I am still unable to offer more than $15,000 for the product.
